data.description: Well maintained home on a serene 2.4 acres. This home features an open floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. The spacious rooms give you plenty of space to add your personal touches. Located on the property is a 30x40 shop on a concrete slab. This home has new carpet in bedrooms, new skirting and fresh paint. If you are looking to enjoy life in the country, you found your new home! Come see for yourself the quality and care that has gone into this home.
